{"word":"G1565 - ἐκεῖνος - ekeînos - ek-i'-nos - He","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκεῖνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekeînos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-i'-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">He</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"அந்த, அது - பிரதி பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the one there"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1563 - ἐκεῖ - ekeî - ek-i'/1563\">G1563</a>; <i>that</i> one (or [neuter] thing); often intensified by the article prefixed: - he, it, the other (same), selfsame, that (same, very), X their, X them, they, this, those. See also <a href=\"#/G3778 - οὗτος - hoûtos - hoo'-tos/3778\">G3778</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}